story.storyDescription: Sarah finds a dead body in the woods and uncovers a dark and deadly mystery.
story.title: Littlefield - Part 5

messages.text: Is this Corrinne Henning?
Who is this?
This is your sister’s friend Wayne
WHAT!?
The same Wayne who was one of the last people to see her before she went missing??
Yes. I’m sorry. I wanted to track you down earlier...
but I didn’t know Sarah’s last name until I saw her picture on the news.
Then tracked you down on Facebook. Are you okay?
Am I doing okay?! No I’m not okay.
I’m writing to you because I might know where she is
WHAT!? Did you tell the cops??
They took down a statement...
but they don’t seem to be doing anything about it
That sounds like a lie, since my best friend’s Dad is the police chief
So if this is a sick joke, fuck off
No…I saw your sister after the party
What? Where??
She texted me while she was walking home in the woods.
She said she saw a dead body and someone was chasing her...
that she wanted me to come get her.
Why did she text you and not call the cops??
She said she was afraid the person chasing her would hear...
so I called the cops…
Anyway, some crazy shit went down and I thought she was dead
So I drove down there anyway, to help the cops on their search for her
And??
I got there. No cops.
And just as I was about to get out of the car to go search myself...
I saw her getting dragged out of the woods and thrown into a black van
WHAT!? Did you see who pulled her in it???
A bunch of people in combat gear
Oh my God….Did you tell the cops this??
Yes, but only described the car to them. No plate numbers.
When I checked in about it, they didn’t seem to do anything about it.
WHAT THE FUCK
I think they were from the army or something…
What!? Why would that make any sense??
I don’t know. It was dark, I could be wrong, but my point currently is that...
I saw this van about fifteen minutes ago.
My friend Kurt and I are following it right now
ARE YOU SERIOUS??
I was going to call the cops to give the plate number...
but thought we’d just see where they go first...
just in case they continue to do jack shit
The police chief is downstairs in my house though
Dirk Sykes?
Yeah…
He was the guy I reported it to
But he said they didn’t have any leads so far
Something is going on
I’m going downstairs to talk to him. Where are you headed
We just got off 95, and we’re going down Harper’s May Rd.
Shit, he’s gone.
Sykes?
Yeah, my Mom said he just had to go for some emergency...
and that we had to stay inside
I’ll text my friend Helena
It seems like we’re pulling up in front of a big gate
They’re pulling inside.
We’re going to try to park down the way, and see what they’re doing
I don’t get it…is it a gate to a mansion? A building?
It’s actually a barn, it looks like. It’s kind of the middle of nowhere.
We’re surrounded by woods. It has security though.
A barn!?
It looks like more people are getting out of the van that got taken.
They’re flipping out about why they’re there
Can you hear what they’re saying
No just that they are really angry
A cop car is coming!
Flag him down!! Tell him they have my sister!!!
We are! He just pulled over and is coming up to the car now.
What’s going on????
Wayne???
Wayne??
He came up to the car and asked what we were doing here
When I told him about your sister.
He said that he’d call it into the station
Didn’t feel urgent about it at all.
Then this fucking man came out of the woods and bit into his neck
What??
The man already looked like he’d been dead for a decade
Oh my God where are you now??
We sped off
Holy shit, there’s more of them
What do you mean!?!?
These people…They’re just wandering the streets
Helena just texted me back...
she just described the same thing was just in her house
We have to go in there and get my sister!! You have to go back!
We won’t be able to get in because of the gate
YOU HAVE TO TRY
I’m sorry I can’t. I need to get back to my family and see if they’re okay!
Wayne!!! Please!!
WAYNE!!!
ANSWER ME!!!!
Click below to see what happens next...
